tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select count(usersessionid) as "Satisfied Users" from usersession where useraction.application="MyApp"  and userExperienceScore="SATISFIED"

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: select count(usersessionid) as "Tolerated Users" from usersession where useraction.application="MyApp"  and userExperienceScore="TOLERATED"

tiles.name: DTAQL
tiles.query: select count(usersessionid) as "Frustrated Users" from usersession where useraction.application="MyApp"  and userExperienceScore="FRUSTRATED"

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select useraction.application,percentile(useraction.duration,90) as "90 Percentile",percentile(useraction.duration,80) as "80 Percentile",percentile(useraction.duration,70) as "70 Percentile",percentile(useraction.duration,60) as "60 Percentile",percentile(useraction.duration,50) as "50 Percentile",percentile(useraction.duration,40) as "40 Percentile",percentile(useraction.duration,30) as "30 Percentile",percentile(useraction.duration,20) as "20 Percentile",percentile(useraction.duration,10) as "10 Percentile"from usersession where useraction.application="MyApp"  group by useraction.application

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select useraction.application,percentile(useraction.visuallycompletetime,90) as "90 Percentile",percentile(useraction.visuallycompletetime,80) as "80 Percentile",percentile(useraction.visuallycompletetime,70) as "70 Percentile",percentile(useraction.visuallycompletetime,60) as "60 Percentile",percentile(useraction.visuallycompletetime,50) as "50 Percentile",percentile(useraction.visuallycompletetime,40) as "40 Percentile",percentile(useraction.visuallycompletetime,30) as "30 Percentile",percentile(useraction.visuallycompletetime,20) as "20 Percentile",percentile(useraction.visuallycompletetime,10) as "10 Percentile"from usersession where useraction.application="MyApp"  group by useraction.application

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select useraction.application,percentile(useraction.speedindex,90) as "90 Percentile",percentile(useraction.speedindex,80) as "80 Percentile",percentile(useraction.speedindex,70) as "70 Percentile",percentile(useraction.speedindex,60) as "60 Percentile",percentile(useraction.speedindex,50) as "50 Percentile",percentile(useraction.speedindex,40) as "40 Percentile",percentile(useraction.speedindex,30) as "30 Percentile",percentile(useraction.speedindex,20) as "20 Percentile",percentile(useraction.speedindex,10) as "10 Percentile"from usersession where useraction.application="MyApp"  group by useraction.application

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select PERCENTILE(duration,90) as "Duration 90th Percentile" from useraction where useraction.application="MyApp"

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select PERCENTILE(visuallyCompleteTime,90) as "Visually Complete 90th Percentile" from useraction where useraction.application="MyApp"

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query: select PERCENTILE(speedIndex,90) as "Speed Index 90th Percentile" from useraction where useraction.application="MyApp"
